@startuml state-member-lifecycle
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam stateFontSize 12

title Member Lifecycle States (Admin Perspective)

[*] --> Registered : User completes\nregistration

Registered --> PendingKyc : Initiates identity\nverification

PendingKyc --> Active : KYC approved\n(auto or manual)
PendingKyc --> Registered : KYC rejected;\nmember may resubmit

Active --> WaitingPeriod : First 3 months\nafter KYC approval
WaitingPeriod --> Active : Waiting period\ncompleted

Active --> Suspended : Admin suspends\n(missed payments,\npolicy violation)
WaitingPeriod --> Suspended : Admin suspends

Suspended --> Active : Admin reactivates;\nwaiting period may reset
Suspended --> Removed : Admin permanently\nremoves member

Active --> Removed : Admin removes\n(fraud, violation)

Removed --> [*]

state Registered : Entry / Account created\nEntry / Email/phone verified
state PendingKyc : Entry / ID + selfie submitted\nDo / Await verification result
state Active : Entry / Full platform access\nEntry / Can contribute and request
state WaitingPeriod : Entry / 3-month countdown\nEntry / Can contribute\nEntry / Cannot request assistance
state Suspended : Entry / All access restricted\nEntry / Notify member with reason\nEntry / Log in audit trail
state Removed : Entry / Account deactivated\nEntry / Data retained 7 years\nEntry / Notify member

@enduml
